OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778191867
OL,3,CArsenal fans face hotel room and air
OL,4,Cfare price hike for Champions League
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FArsenal supporters booking hotel rooms
OL,8,Ffor the Champions League final in
OL,9,FHungary are facing fees more than 18
OL,10,Ftimes higher than normal.
OL,12,FThousands of the north London club's
OL,13,Fsupporters will descend on Budapest
OL,14,Ffor the match on May 30, following the
OL,15,Fteam's semi-final victory on Tuesday.
OL,17,FMost hotels in Budapest are already
OL,18,Ffully booked and those with
OL,19,Favailability are charging high prices.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778191867
OL,3,CArsenal fans face hotel room and air
OL,4,Cfare price hike for Champions League
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FAnalysis by the Press Association
OL,8,Ffound a twin or double room for two
OL,9,Fpeople at the Expo Tower Hotel on the
OL,10,Fnight of the match costs 1,458 euros
OL,11,F(#1,259).
OL,13,FThis is more than 18 times the price
OL,14,Fof 73 euros (#63) for arriving a day
OL,15,Flater.
OL,17,FAt Bohem Art Hotel, the cost is 1,618
OL,18,Feuros (#1,396) for staying on May 30,
OL,19,Fand 113 euros (#98) the following day.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778191867
OL,3,CArsenal fans face hotel room and air
OL,4,Cfare price hike for Champions League
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FHotel President is charging #886 on
OL,8,FMay 30, and #104 on May 31.
OL,10,FAccommodation website Booking.com is
OL,11,Fwarning consumers searching for a
OL,12,Fhotel room in Budapest on May 30 that
OL,13,F"99% of places to stay are unavailable
OL,14,Ffor your dates on our site".
OL,16,FAkhil Vyas of the Arsenal Supporters'
OL,17,FTrust said: "You're talking a lot of
OL,18,Fmoney."
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@[O]yD@MOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778191867
OL,3,CArsenal fans face hotel room and air
OL,4,Cfare price hike for Champions League
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FAsked if he thought the price of hotel
OL,8,Frooms was fair, he replied: "I
OL,9,Fwouldn't say so. It's cheeky.
OL,11,F"I get it, it's business, (but) how
OL,12,Fgreat is it for Budapest to have a
OL,13,FChampions League final there, with all
OL,14,Fthe tourism?
OL,16,F"It might put people off."
OL,26,@pD@]OUsD@AOUxD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778191867
OL,3,CArsenal fans face hotel room and air
OL,4,Cfare price hike for Champions League
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FMr Vyas called for company bosses to
OL,8,Fbe "a bit more sensible" about
OL,9,Fpricing, but said: "There's no
OL,10,Fregulation or anything like that, so
OL,11,Fpeople can ultimately do what they
OL,12,Fwant."
OL,14,FHe predicted that prices may fall
OL,15,Fslightly after rooms are cancelled by
OL,16,Fsupporters of whichever team loses the
OL,17,Fsecond semi-final on Wednesday night
OL,18,Fbetween Bayern Munich and Paris Saint-
OL,19,FGermain.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@XO]qD@TOUtD@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
