PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778191867
OL,3,CArsenal fans face hotel room and air
OL,4,Cfare price hike for Champions League
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FArsenal supporters booking flights to
OL,8,FBudapest are also facing high prices.
OL,10,FThe cheapest easyJet flight from
OL,11,FGatwick to the city costs #519 on the
OL,12,Fday of the match, compared with #58 on
OL,13,FMay 31.
OL,15,FWizz Air has a flight from Luton to
OL,16,FBudapest costing from #462, whereas
OL,17,Fflying a day later is possible for #46.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778191867
OL,3,CArsenal fans face hotel room and air
OL,4,Cfare price hike for Champions League
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FSupporters wanting to fly with British
OL,8,FAirways and arrive in time to get to
OL,9,Fthe match must travel two days early,
OL,10,Fon May 28.
OL,12,FA flight on that day costs from #740,
OL,13,Fcompared with #96 on May 31.
OL,15,FMr Vyas said: "It's the Champions
OL,16,FLeague final at the end of the day so
OL,17,Fpeople will do it, including me."
OL,26,@wD@OOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
