FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778191867
OL,3,CArsenal fans face hotel room and air
OL,4,Cfare price hike for Champions League
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FFans can save money by booking
OL,8,Findirect flights, flying to other
OL,9,Flocations and completing the journey
OL,10,Fto Budapest by train, or even
OL,11,Ftravelling by coach.
OL,13,FCoach operator Coach Innovations is
OL,14,Foffering return trips from London to
OL,15,FBudapest for #339, leaving on the
OL,16,Fevening of May 28 and arriving by 10am
OL,17,Fon May 30.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
