FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778191867
OL,3,CArsenal fans face hotel room and air
OL,4,Cfare price hike for Champions League
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FThis involves a cross-Channel ferry
OL,8,Fsailing from Dover to Calais, and
OL,9,Ftravelling through France, Belgium,
OL,10,FGermany and Austria.
OL,12,FThe Coach Innovations website suggests
OL,13,Fpassengers will "sleep for a week"
OL,14,Fafter the return journey.
OL,16,FArsenal said they have received an
OL,17,Fallocation of 16,824 general admission
OL,18,Ftickets for the match at the Puskas
OL,19,FArena, which has a capacity of more
OL,20,Fthan 67,000.
OL,26,@uD@QOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
