PN,40710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778191867
OL,3,CArsenal fans face hotel room and air
OL,4,Cfare price hike for Champions League
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FTickets will be made available based
OL,8,Fon supporters' previous attendance at
OL,9,Fmatches, costing from 70 euros (#60).
OL,11,FReselling website ticombo is offering
OL,12,Ftickets for the match from #5,177.
OL,14,FOther English football supporters also
OL,15,Fface high bills for European finals in
OL,16,Fthe current weeks.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
