PN,40711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1778191867
OL,3,CArsenal fans face hotel room and air
OL,4,Cfare price hike for Champions League
OL,5,Cfinal
OL,7,FThousands of fans of Aston Villa or
OL,8,FNottingham Forest ` whichever team
OL,9,Fwins their semi-final clash ` will
OL,10,Ftravel to Istanbul, Turkey for the
OL,11,FEuropa League final on May 20.
OL,13,FMany Crystal Palace supporters will
OL,14,Ftravel to Leipzig, Germany for the
OL,15,FConference League final on May 27 if
OL,16,Fthe team makes it through their semi-
OL,17,Ffinal.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/12
